<title>A CALL FOR REAPERS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kawl kimvela buh umte chuh,
 Lakkhawm phat a hung hitai;
 Mun gam la leh anai ale,
 A bawnin a min zotai.

[V2]
 Lalpa, buh at ding hun sawlin!
 Ka hun ngetnau hi ngaiin;
 Buhphal lakhawm ding hun sawlin,
 Lakkhawm phat a kikhelh ma'n.

[V3]
 2. Zingkal tung leh sun lai inle,
 Nisa tum ding kuon inle;
 Mun tina buh lakhawm dingin,
 Nasem ding mi sawldawk in.

[V4]
 3. Kinmeng in, buh kuoi ding ei tai,
 Sana buhvui lakhawm in;
 Atawpa van In na zawt tieng,
 Kipak takin tung inla.</lyrics>
</song>